songs.title: Déjà Vu
songs.lyrics:
From Snippet:

[Chorus]
Déjà Vu
I see me and you (Heh)
You're the only thing I can never lose (Heh, heh)
Lose you, I will lose me too (Heh)
Full moon, edges at the move
Déjà Vu
I see me and you (Heh)
You're the only thing I can never lose (Heh, heh)
Lose you, I will lose me too (Heh)
Full moon, edges at the move

[Verse]
Know love she love me lot
On and off, keep on running back
Bitch I want my bag
Canceled all the middle man
I do knocks on wall
I swear I can never land
Smoke my sorrows though
Drown in my sorrow (Oh, woah, oh)
Drown in my sorrow (Oh, woah, oh)
